        BOGOSORT PROGRAM IN COMIT

START   (3 1 4 1 5 9 2 6)     =
        $$ MOVE UNSORTED LIST TO WORKSPACE

CHEK    CHECK $$ IF SORTED GOTO DONE
        SORT $$
        GOTO CHEK

CHECK   SEARCH $1 $2 FOR PAIR WHERE $1 > $2
        RETURN UNSORTED OR SORTED

SORT    SHUFFLE RANDOMLY $$
        RETURN

DONE    PRINT $$
        END
